      <title>红龙虾老板通过实现 ESG 目标降低债券息票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/red-lobster-owner-lowers-bond-coupon-rates-by-meeting-esg-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拥有 Red Lobster Management LLC 的泰国海鲜供应商表示，它已经实现了三个 ESG 目标，从而降低了其可持续发展相关债券的利率。]]></description>
